summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds and/or easements to portions of Tracts 72, 73, 74, 75, 76 and 77, Brighton Beach Acre Tracts; to portions of Blocks 1 and 2, Brighton Beach Orchard Add.; to portions of Blks. 13 and 14 Hillman City Division No. 6; to portions of Tracts 70, 74 and 75, Kelsey's Brighton Beach Acre Tracts; to portion of Lot 1, Ulferts Add.; and to portion of the southeast one-quarter of Section 27, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., for hydrant and/or street purposes and laying off 40th and 42nd Avenues South. (40th Avenue South, et al; Paving, etc.; LID 6617)
